data.description: Turn special moments with the with the entire family into events. This home has plenty of space for your local and out of town family. If the 5 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms along with 3 family rooms isn't enough, there is a bonus room in the basement you can use as a bunk room. You and your family can take full advantage of the indoor sauna and hot tub, and large deck with balcony. The centrally located kitchen can funnel every single delicious meal to all those smiling faces in your life. Finding anything comparable for under 340K with a location like this one isn't going to come easily. You're not just buying a home, you're creating memories. Seller is also offering $5,000 towards Buyer's closing costs and prepaids.
